<TextBlock Margin="5,5,5,5" ToolTip="{Binding Source={StaticResource Settings}, Path=datFolderPath}" Style="{StaticResource ConfigTextBox}" Grid.Row="1" Grid.Column="0" Grid.ColumnSpan="2" Text="Hover to view selected dat folder path"/>
